sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as ML Application /<br/>Notebook
    participant Online as Feature Server (Online)<br/>6567/TCP HTTPS
    participant SecMgr as SecurityManager<br/>(OIDC / K8s RBAC)
    participant OnlineDB as Online Store<br/>(Redis/PostgreSQL)
    participant OfflineDB as Offline Store<br/>(BigQuery/DuckDB)
    participant CronJob as CronJob (ose-cli)<br/>Materialization
    participant Operator as Feast Operator<br/>Go Controller
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,OnlineDB: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval

    Client->>Online: POST /get-online-features<br/>HTTPS/TLS (service-serving certs)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OIDC/K8s)
    Online->>SecMgr: Validate token & RBAC<br/>inject_user_details
    SecMgr->>K8sAPI: TokenReview (K8s auth mode)
    K8sAPI-->>SecMgr: Token valid + user info
    SecMgr->>OIDC: JWKS retrieval (OIDC auth mode)
    OIDC-->>SecMgr: JWKS keys
    SecMgr-->>Online: READ_ONLINE authorized
    Online->>OnlineDB: Read features<br/>TCP/TLS (configurable)<br/>Auth: Store credentials
    OnlineDB-->>Online: Feature values
    Online-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/TLS

    Note over CronJob,OnlineDB: Flow 2: Feature Materialization (CronJob)

    CronJob->>Online: POST /materialize<br/>HTTPS/TLS<br/>Auth: Intra-communication token
    Online->>OfflineDB: Read historical features<br/>TCP/HTTPS/TLS<br/>Auth: Store credentials
    OfflineDB-->>Online: Historical feature data
    Online->>OnlineDB: Write materialized features<br/>TCP/TLS<br/>Auth: Store credentials
    OnlineDB-->>Online: Write confirmed
    Online-->>CronJob: 200 OK

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Notebook ConfigMap Injection

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch Notebook CRs<br/>HTTPS/TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Notebook with<br/>opendatahub.io/feast-integration: "true"
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Read FeatureStore client ConfigMap<br/>HTTPS/TLS
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: feature_store.yaml config
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update {notebook}-feast-config ConfigMap<br/>HTTPS/TLS
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: ConfigMap created
